CADI.Client.Session

Class ClientJPIPChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • CADI.Common.Session.JPIPChannel
      • CADI.Client.Session.ClientJPIPChannel

  • public class ClientJPIPChannel
extends JPIPChannel
    This class is used to save the channel properties.

    For further information about JPIP channels, see ISO/IEC 15444-9 section B.2

    Version:
    1.0.2 2010/01/25
    Author:
    Group on Interactive Coding of Images (GICI)

    • Field Detail

      • localCID

        private java.lang.String localCID
        It is a local channel identifier. It is better to use this channel identifier instead of the JPIPChannel.cid because the value of the latter one is set by the server, and it could not be set. However, the localCID is set by the constructor of the object.

      • generateCID

        protected java.lang.String generateCID()
        Generates a unique channel identifier. The unique identifier generation is base on the current time, it is a time-stamp.

        NOTICE: this method could be improved adding the Rijndael (or another one), client information, etc. to improve the security.

        Returns:
        the unique channel identifier.
